  "body": "This has been discussed on Telegram, just adding it here.\r\n\r\nI'm creating a tool which among other things has a generator for a Buidler setup. Would make this less hacky if Buidler could allow source outside Buidler folder.\r\n\r\n## Error\r\n\r\nBDLR401: Tried to import file outside your project\r\n\r\nOne of your projects tried to import a file that it's outside your Buidler project.\r\n\r\nThis is disabled for security reasons.\r\n\r\n_Thank you again for Buidler, its the best!_\r\n\r\n",
